ZH: 地理是关于地球表面的研究。
EN: Geography is the study of the Earth's surface.

ZH: 地理包括人类活动对环境的影响。
EN: Geography includes the impact of human activities on the environment.

ZH: 我很喜欢学习地理。
EN: I really enjoy studying geography.

ZH: 地理知识有助于我们了解世界。
EN: Geographic knowledge helps us understand the world.

ZH: 我们学校的地理老师很有趣。
EN: Our geography teacher at school is very interesting.

ZH: 地理探索推动科技的发展。
EN: Geographic exploration drives the development of technology.

ZH: 孩子们通过地理课学习了不同的文化。
EN: Children learn about different cultures through geography classes.

ZH: 地理研究有助于我们预测自然灾害。
EN: Geographic research helps us predict natural disasters.

ZH: 地理是一个跨学科的领域。
EN: Geography is an interdisciplinary field.

ZH: 大自然的奇观使地理更加有趣。
EN: Natural wonders make geography even more interesting.

ZH: 地理信息系统在测绘工作中被广泛应用。
EN: Geographic information systems are widely used in surveying work.

ZH: 我们要为下周的地理考试做准备。
EN: We need to prepare for the geography exam next week.

ZH: 他的爱好是环游世界，研究各地的地理。
EN: His hobby is to travel around the world and study the geography of different places.

ZH: 我的父母给我买了一本地理书。
EN: My parents bought me a geography book.

ZH: 地理教育对培养学生的全球意识很重要。
EN: Geographic education is important for cultivating students' global awareness.

ZH: 地理促进了各国之间的文化交流。
EN: Geography promotes cultural exchange between countries.

ZH: 他的地理知识使他成为一名优秀的导游。
EN: His knowledge of geography makes him an excellent tour guide.

ZH: 这个国家的地理特点是多样的。
EN: The geographic features of this country are diverse.

ZH: 地理位置决定了一个地区的气候。
EN: Geographic location determines the climate of a region.
